        </item>
        <item>
            <title>世博展全球首部 AI 自動洗澡機   15 分鐘完成洗澡超療癒感受</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-bath-tube</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 27 Apr 2025 08:23:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305117</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>2025 年大阪世博會上，日本企業 Science 正式展示他們的 AI 自動洗澡機「ミライ人間洗濯機」，結合人工智能與感應技術，讓洗澡成為一場身心靈放鬆的療癒旅程。這部外形酷似戰機駕駛艙的裝置，利用智能系統即時調節水流和溫度，並播放短片，讓使用者在短短 15 分鐘內享受多感官的舒緩體驗。設計靈感取自 1970 年大阪萬博展示過的超聲波浴缸，展望未來生活方式的同時，也為洗浴設備注入嶄新元素。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305126" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>這台 AI 自動洗澡機外觀設計充滿未來感，擁有一個可開啟的透明罩，吸引大量參觀者駐足觀賞。當體驗者跨入機艙，透明罩緩緩關閉，洗澡過程正式展開。整個過程由 AI 系統全程監控，透過感應器即時測量使用者心跳、情緒等身體數據，並根據個人狀況靈活調整水流強度與水溫，確保每位使用者獲得最適合自身狀態的洗浴體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開始注水</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲利用感應器測量心跳，根據精神狀態播放音樂和影像</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲浴缸內充滿潔白的泡沫</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲微細氣泡技術可產生泡沫，將污垢浮起並沖洗全身</p><p>透明罩正面設有顯示屏幕，除了即時反映使用者的身體狀態數據，還同步播放舒壓短片，令整個洗澡過程更加放鬆。該機器備有三種模式可供選擇，包括展現日本四季景色的庭園、五彩繽紛的海底世界，及遼闊無垠的鳥瞰天空，讓每次洗澡都能依心情自由切換，享受視覺與身體的雙重放鬆。</p><p>Science 董事長青山恭明指出，這款洗澡機採用公司自家開發的 Mirable 微細氣泡技術，有效潔淨皮膚同時呵護肌膚健康。他強調，這部洗澡機不單向 1970 年大阪萬博展出的超聲波浴缸致敬，更期望透過科技改善日常生活質素，開啟未來洗浴新時代。</p><p>目前 Science 已開放 1000 個體驗名額，全數成功登記。未來是否投入市場銷售，仍有待進一步公佈。這款 AI 自動洗澡機展示了日本企業在結合科技與生活層面的創新思維，為日常沐浴習慣帶來全新可能。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_35717"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dyw6s1n3n_k?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/">世博展全球首部 AI 自動洗澡機   15 分鐘完成洗澡超療癒感受</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
